                     rdfs:label "tunnel"@en ,
                                "тоннель"@ru ,
                                "туннель"@kz .


###  http://ontogeo.kz/geont-kz#Ultimate_foundation_deformations
:Ultimate_foundation_deformations rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://ontogeo.kz/geont-kz#Ultimate_foundation_deformations_Concept
